  "base_path": "/get-birthday-anniversary-message-from-king",
  "content_id": "3eaa7adb-d264-4548-bd6b-414aa2145fd1",
  "description": "Get a message (telegram) from the King and the Queen Consort - birthdays and anniversaries that qualify, documents you need.",
  "details": {
    "body": "<p>You can get a free birthday or anniversary message from the King and the Queen Consort for a <a href=\"/types-of-british-nationality\">British national</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"birthdays\">Birthdays</h2>\n\n<p>You can get a message for someone’s:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>100th birthday</li>\n  <li>105th birthday</li>\n  <li>birthday each year following their 105th</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"if-the-person-gets-a-state-pension-or-other-benefit-and-lives-in-the-uk\">If the person gets a State Pension or other benefit and lives in the UK</h3>\n\n<p>You do not need to apply for a birthday message.</p>\n\n<p>This will be sent using the name and address on the person’s State Pension or other benefit record.</p>\n\n<p>To update a State Pension record, <a href=\"/contact-pension-service\">contact the Pension Service</a>.</p>\n\n<p>To update any other benefit record, <a href=\"/report-benefits-change-circumstances\">report a change in circumstances</a>.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"if-the-person-does-not-get-a-state-pension-or-other-benefit-or-does-not-live-in-the-uk\">If the person does not get a State Pension or other benefit or does not live in the UK</h3>\n\n<p>You need to apply for a message. You can apply:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>no earlier than 5 weeks before the birthday date</li>\n  <li>up to 6 months after for a belated message</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://apply.royal.uk/Apply/PreAppBirthday.jsp\">Apply for a birthday message online</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Find out more, including how to apply by post, on the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.royal.uk/anniversary-messages-0\">Royal website</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"anniversaries\">Anniversaries</h2>\n\n<p>You can get a message for a couple’s:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>60th (diamond) anniversary</li>\n  <li>65th anniversary</li>\n  <li>70th (platinum) anniversary</li>\n  <li>anniversary each year following their 70th</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>You can apply:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>no earlier than 5 weeks before the anniversary date if you apply online, or 3 weeks before if you apply by post</li>\n  <li>up to 6 months after for a belated message</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>You’ll need to send a copy of the couple’s marriage certificate when you apply.</p>\n\n<p><a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://apply.royal.uk/Apply/PreAppWeddingAnniversary.jsp\">Apply for an anniversary message online</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Find out more, including how to apply by post, on the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.royal.uk/anniversary-messages-0\">Royal website</a>.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"if-you-do-not-have-a-copy-of-the-marriage-certificate-and-the-couple-got-married-in-england-or-wales\">If you do not have a copy of the marriage certificate and the couple got married in England or Wales</h3>\n\n<p>Call the General Register Office to apply 8 weeks before the anniversary.</p>\n\n<p>You’ll need:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the names of the couple</li>\n  <li>their current address</li>\n  <li>the date and place of the marriage</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The General Register Office will confirm the details and request the anniversary message for you.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p>General Register Office<br>\nTelephone: 0300 123 1837<br>\nTextphone: 18001 0300 123 1837<br>\nMonday to Friday, 8am to 8pm<br>\nSaturday, 9am to 4pm<br>\n<a href=\"/call-charges\">Find out about call charges</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h3 id=\"if-you-do-not-have-a-copy-of-the-marriage-certificate-and-the-couple-got-married-in-scotland-or-northern-ireland\">If you do not have a copy of the marriage certificate and the couple got married in Scotland or Northern Ireland</h3>\n\n<p>There are <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.nrscotland.gov.uk/registration/royal-anniversary-messages\">different processes in Scotland</a> and <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.nidirect.gov.uk/articles/congratulatory-messages\">in Northern Ireland</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"if-the-person-lives-in-australia-canada-or-new-zealand\">If the person lives in Australia, Canada or New Zealand</h2>\n\n<p>You must apply directly to the Governor-General. For contact details call the Anniversaries Office.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p>Anniversaries Office<br>\nTelephone: 020 7930 4832<br>\nMonday to Friday, 9am to 5pm<br>\n<a href=\"/call-charges\">Find out about call charges</a></p>\n</div>\n",
